<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.baseHeadContent %>

    <title><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A celebrity quiz game! Pick your desired quiz size, answer the questions, and see how you did at the end! But most importantly... have fun!"
    />
  </head>

  <body class="project-page">
    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.preBodyContent %>

    <a class="home-link" href="/">Home</a>

    <div class="header">
      <img
        class="emoji"
        src="<%= require('../../assets/projects/emoji/shooting-star.svg') %>"
        width="70"
        height="70"
      />
      <h1><%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <ul class="badge-list">
        <li>2021</li>
        <li>Gatsby</li>
        <li>GraphQL</li>
        <li>Apollo</li>
        <li>FaunaDB</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        A celebrity quiz game! Pick your desired quiz size, answer the
        questions, and see how you did at the end! But most importantly... have
        fun!
      </p>

      <p style="text-decoration: line-through">Check it out!</p>
      <p style="font-style: italic">
        ðŸ‘† The hosted site is curently under construction due to the deprectaion
        of Gatsby Cloud and the Fauna GraphQL API.
      </p>

      <p>
        As a part of this project, I also created a simple CMS - my partner
        created and sourced all of the content.
      </p>

      <p>
        Source code in the
        <a
          href="https://github.com/JesseKuntz/if-they-were-this"
          target="_blank"
          >Github repository</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.postBodyContent %>
  </body>
</html>
